business requirements:

BR-01: Product Browsing
  The system should allow users to view a list of available products.
  Users should be able to view details of a selected product.

BR-02: Product Search and Categories
  The system should allow users to search for products.
  The system should allow users to view products by category.

BR-03: User Login
  The system should allow registered users to log in.
  The system should prevent access to certain features without login.

BR-04: Shopping Cart
  The system should allow users to add products to a shopping cart.
  Users should be able to view and manage items in the cart.

BR-05: Checkout
  The system should allow users to proceed to checkout with items in the cart.
  The system should show order confirmation after checkout.

BR-06: Error Handling
  The system should display appropriate messages when an action fails.
  The system should handle invalid inputs gracefully.




